{"tid":1545708,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"關於舉報假新聞/未經證實消息","createTime":"2019-09-06T04:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T05:20:08.000Z","uid":14091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87e6a3a5c2c2b8f3cc51e5d7f0a6df23d2d9152b","tid":1545708,"uid":14091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"首先利申 我唔知依加自殺post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個玩法係點<br />\n<br />\n不過針對fake news橫行，我有2個建議<br />\n<br />\n1. 將舉報分類，仿傚facebook做法，可以揀假新聞/未經證實消息/自殺相關etc.咁，依加要手打原因同email可能唔夠方便，亦都難以analyse，當然可以兩樣都keep，本身無衝突<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果多人report就好似自殺相關post咁有個置頂banner咁，話多人舉報為假新聞咁，當然admin都可以最後把關，同埋懷疑假新聞嘅post即使上咗熱門都要放最底<br />\n<br />\n當然為咗防止有人惡意report，可能可以限制P牌無得report，或者多次惡意report嘅account限制只可以手打原因唔可以揀投訴分類，增高投訴門檻咁。"},{"pid":"ffba3c31795391c06b5b1d8725d42a147f85a4c1","tid":1545708,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86cd3216a5daa037f7f8068b71e6040e3b36a96f","tid":1545708,"uid":14091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffba3c31795391c06b5b1d8725d42a147f85a4c1","tid":1545708,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"